A Federal House of Representative member, Hon. Bello Dantine Yellow, has been confirmed dead. Confirming his death to newsmen at Govnerment House, Birnin Kebbi, the chief Press Secretary to the Kebbi State Governor, Alhaji Muazu Dakingari, said that the late lawmaker who represented Yauri /Shanga Federal constituency of Birnin Kebbi, died at National Hospital Abuja after a brief illness. The late Dantine Yellow was a former State House of Assembly member and chairman Shanga Local of Kebbi State and member House Committee on electoral matters. He was aged 57.